      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Bash the <strong>lemongrass</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Remove the tough outer layer<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> of the <strong>lemongrass</strong> and chop the softer inner core roughly</p><p>Peel and roughly chop <strong>1</strong> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
