    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>lemongrass</strong> to a <strong>food processor </strong>with the<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> ground coriander</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cinnamon</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> cold water </strong>and blitz into a smooth paste – this is your<strong> Khao Soi curry paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
